HELLO-NIGHTMARE
---------------

HOW TO BUILD

  $ ./autogen.sh
  $ ./configure
  $ make
  # make install

HOW TO CLEAN

  $ make clean (for binary only)
  or
  $ make distclean (for all generated files)

HOW TO REMOVE

  # make uninstall

